text: August Kuehn House was a historic home located in downtown Evansville, Indiana. It was built in 1864. Note: This includes , , and Accompanying photographs It has been demolished. It was listed on the National Register of Historic Places in 1982. ==References== Category:Houses on the National Register of Historic Places in Indiana Category:Houses completed in 1864 Category:National Register of Historic Places in Evansville, Indiana Category:Houses in Evansville, Indiana
